data.description: Beautiful tri level home in desirable Woodridge! The home has been upgraded with wood look tile, 5'' baseboards, white kitchen cabinets, quartz countertops and much more! Appliances are stainless steel. Split floorplan. Two bedrooms & bath upstairs, One bedroom, bath, family room & laundry, down stairs. The Kitchen, living & dining combo with fireplace are on the main level. Large side yard with gorgeous pool, double gate RV and single gate RV on west side. No HOA!
